Photos by @ryanresatka, unbelievable work dude!

node.text:
Perched precariously over a 2000ft over a glacier in a 90 year old isn’t a recipe for a peaceful nights sleep, but those first rays of make you forget it all. 🤤
Photos & story by @alexstrohl, thanks for sharing this!
